250
00:14:23,298 --> 00:14:27,798
If you remove the "fish" part from all the kanji characters...

251
00:14:27,798 --> 00:14:29,498
Ao.

252
00:14:29,498 --> 00:14:31,598
Sato.

253
00:14:31,598 --> 00:14:33,798
Shu.

254
00:14:33,798 --> 00:14:34,898
Hei.

255
00:14:34,898 --> 00:14:37,798
